00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:14.880
[Previously]
I can feel there’s also someone else in this house.

00:00:17.440 --> 00:00:18.280
Are you all right, dear?

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:21.160
You can see him, Khun Kaew?

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:23.280
Of course, I can see him. I have eyes.

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:27.880
Is it possible that someone I saw in my dream,

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:30.120
would also exist in real life as if they are the same person?

00:00:30.680 --> 00:00:32.159
Is there something you want to talk to me?

00:00:32.680 --> 00:00:33.360
What?

00:00:33.360 --> 00:00:35.520
But it looks like you’re waiting for me to come out of my room.

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:37.800
Are you following me, Khun Yai?

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:41.360
We’re probably destined to meet wherever we go.

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:44.720
Ruedee, why do you want to see me?

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:48.560
My cousin, Sophee, wants you to draw for her.

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:54.360
But Ruedee, you also know, don’t you?

00:00:55.480 --> 00:00:58.440
That I can’t draw a portrait.

00:00:59.160 --> 00:01:02.760
I know. I already tried to refuse it for you.

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:06.800
But she still insisted she used to see a portrait you drew.

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:10.440
That’s why she really wants you to draw for her.

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:11.800
Where did she see it?

00:01:13.160 --> 00:01:13.960
I wonder too.

00:01:14.560 --> 00:01:19.000
I’m also curious but I was too scared to ask.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:23.000
So, my mother told me to ask you first.

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:26.640
I really want to help you, Ruedee.

00:01:27.400 --> 00:01:29.240
But what if I say yes…

00:01:30.280 --> 00:01:32.240
and end up unable to draw it?

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:36.000
Then don’t do it. Don’t say yes.

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:39.000
I don’t want you to draw for her anyway.

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:50.440
But…will you get into trouble if I don’t do it?

00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:52.240
Isn’t she your cousin?

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:54.920
Who cares? I can’t be bothered.

00:01:55.280 --> 00:01:57.120
Let’s not do it then.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:02:00.240
It’s better to stay away from her.

00:02:06.160 --> 00:02:07.120
So…

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:10.360
How did you get here?

00:02:10.919 --> 00:02:12.360
Did your driver take you here?

00:02:12.920 --> 00:02:14.480
Oh my goodness.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:16.480
I totally forgot.

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:23.440
[Idolfactory]

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:26.520
[Workpoint]

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:29.000
